scalable production, regulatory precision, and deep scientific expertise, we support partners in both regulated and semi-regulated markets.</div><div class="pbmit-heading-desc">Our Vizag Unit 2 API Facility is approved by major global regulatory agencies, including the USFDA, WHO-GMP EDQM, and KFDA. These certifications are a testament to our commitment to quality, safety, and adherence to international manufacturing standards. Additionally, our compliance with CDSCO and other Indian regulatory bodies ensures transparency and efficiency in domestic operations.</div><div class="pbmit-heading-desc">At Emnar, we emphasise cost-effective process development, route-of-synthesis optimisation, and strict impurity profiling, backed by a strong R&amp;D and analytical team. Our API portfolio spans multiple therapeutic segments, and we actively file Drug Master Files (DMFs) to support regulatory submissions for our partners.</div><div class="pbmit-heading-desc">From laboratory-scale innovation to full-scale commercial production, Emnar Pharma is built to serve your API needs with integrity, speed, and reliability.</div><div class="pt-3 mobile-about-list-inside"><a class="pbmit-btn pbmit-btn-blackish-custom" href="contact-us.php"><span class="pbmit-button-content-wrapper"><span class="pbmit-button-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 60 60"><path d="m31 50.979c-.362.007-.727-.081-1.049-.28-.929-.572-1.212-1.814-.653-2.742.047-.082 5.886-9.826 17.032-15.958h-43.33c-1.103 0-2-.897-2-2s.897-2 2-2h43.33c-11.084-6.097-16.989-15.884-17.047-15.982-.547-.934-.244-2.177.689-2.73.946-.561 2.192-.236 2.757.715.909 1.45 9.433 14.449 24.722 18.046.915.225 1.549 1.026 1.549 1.952s-.63 1.729-1.532 1.948c-15.354 3.61-23.849 16.626-24.767 18.099-.36.577-1.025.919-1.7.932z"></path></svg> </span><span class="pbmit-button-text about-text-custom">Connect with Us</span></span></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="our-history-section" class="timeline-sec